聆听 Pnau 和 Empire Of The Sun 合作的“AEIOU” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-pnau-and-empire-of-the-sun-team-up-for-aeiou-3513904?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-普瑙与太阳帝国联手攻克 AEIOUTom Skinner Thu, 12 Oct 2023 12:33:40 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3513904 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Pnau 和 Empire Of The Sun 的 Nick Littlemore 在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “让它带你到舞池”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-pnau-and-empire-of-the-sun-team-up-for-aeiou-3513904">《Listen to Pnau》和 Empire Of The Sun 合作制作《AEIOU》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Pnau 和 Empire Of The Sun 的 Nick Littlemore 在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/NickLittlemore-Pnau-Empire-Of-The-Sun-collaboration-AEIOU-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/pnau">Pnau</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/empire-of-the-sun">Empire Of The Sun</a>联手推出了新的合作单曲“AEIOU”——请在下面查看。</p><p>两个澳大利亚乐队均以创作型歌手尼克·利特尔摩尔 (Nick Littlemore) 为主角。他组成了 EOTS 的一半（由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luke-steele">Luke Steele</a>完成），并与 Peter Mayes 和他的兄弟 Sam Littlemore 一起领导 Pnau。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/luke-steele-empire-of-the-sun-woody-harrelson-owen-wilson-3274839">《我的一生：太阳帝国》原声带 卢克·斯蒂尔</a></strong></li></ul><p>《AEIOU》标志着这两个项目首次结合在一起，并将出现在 Pnau 的第六张录音室专辑《Hyperbolic》中，该专辑预计将于明年初发行。</p><p> “这对我们来说是一个梦想的记录。早在我们遇到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿[约翰]</a>之前，我们就有了创作一首基于元音的歌曲的想法，但直到现在才最终实现，”尼克·利特莫尔在一份声明中解释道。</p><p> “事实证明，等待是值得的。我们终于以出色的方式呈现了与 Empire Of The Sun 的合作！独一无二的声音，让它带你进入舞池。”</p><p> 《太阳帝国》的卢克·斯蒂尔补充道：“这首歌是关于不让我们内心的伊甸园被世界腐蚀。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="PNAU，太阳帝国 - AEIOU（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/B8B2W7iCNA0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首歌的官方动画视频由 MELT Studios 制作，人工智能版本的利特莫尔和斯蒂尔一起踏上了狂野的星际冒险之旅。在上面的剪辑中观看它的展开。</p><p> MELT 体验总监库巴·马蒂卡 (Kuba Matyka) 表示：“《AEIOU》不仅仅是一首歌；它更是一首歌。”这是一次视觉和听觉之旅，将人类创造力、AI 动作捕捉、手工制作 3D 动画和稳定扩散的进步与 Pnau x Empire of the Sun 的艺术融为一体。</p><p> “我们不仅讲述了一个故事，还为其注入了数字生命，反映了这些标志性音乐家的强大重聚，并创造了一个与他们的遗产产生共鸣的传奇故事。”</p><p>正如 Littlemore 在声明中提到的，Pnau 在 2021 年与 Elton John 合作了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/dua-lipa-and-elton-john-preview-new-collaboration-cold-heart-listen-3016861">《Cold Heart》</a> 。最近，三人组<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/check-out-pnau-and-troye-sivans-new-collaborative-single-you-know-what-i-need-3359242">与 Troye Sivan 合作制作了歌曲《You Know What I Need》</a> ，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bebe-rexha">贝比·雷克萨 (Bebe Rexha)</a>和奥祖纳 (Ozuna) 出演<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aox5s2s_SEI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《Stars》</a> 。</p><p>有关即将推出的“双曲线”的更多细节尚未透露。 Pnau 的第五张也是最新的录音室专辑《Changa》于 2017 年发行。与此同时，Empire Of The Sun 于 2016 年发行了他们的第三张也是最新的唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/empire-sun-two-vines-review-1780736">《Two Vines》</a> 。</p><p>去年卢克·斯蒂尔分享了他的首张个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/empire-of-the-suns-luke-steele-announces-new-solo-album-3151945">“Listen To The Water”</a> 。该专辑包含单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/empire-of-the-suns-luke-steele-shares-new-single-armageddon-slice-3178723">“Armageddon Slice”</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/luke-steele-new-single-pool-of-love-3189169">“Pool Of Love”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/empire-of-the-suns-luke-steele-shares-woozy-ballad-running-running-3198325">“Running, Running”</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-pnau-and-empire-of-the-sun-team-up-for-aeiou-3513904">《Listen to Pnau》和 Empire Of The Sun 合作制作《AEIOU》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
